---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection';
import Reviews from '../../components/Reviews';
import ServiceForm from '../../components/ServiceForm';
import LicenseBadges from '../../components/LicenseBadges.astro';
import BrandsSection from '../../components/BrandsSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="HVAC Services in Irvine, CA | HiLo Heating & Air" description="Expert AC repair, furnace repair, and HVAC services in Irvine, CA. Same-day service from licensed technicians at HiLo Heating & Air.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-blue-800 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Air Conditioning Repair Irvine & Furnace Repair Irvine</h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Irvine swings between two extremes — brutal summer heat, then nights in winter that catch people off guard. HiLo Heating and Air handles both.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <LicenseBadges />
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block bg-brand-blue/10 text-brand-blue text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">Schedule Service</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-4">Get a Free Estimate</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Fill out the form and our team will get back to you within 15 minutes. Same-day service available.</p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Same-Day Service Available</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Free Diagnostics with Repair</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Upfront Pricing, No Hidden Fees</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ServiceForm client:load />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>



    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mt-0 mb-4">AC &amp; Furnace Repair in Irvine</h2>

        <p>Irvine swings between two extremes — brutal summer heat, then nights in winter that catch people off guard. Your system has to handle both. When it doesn't, that's where we come in. HiLo Heating and Air does <strong>air conditioning repair Irvine</strong> homeowners call us for all summer, and <strong>furnace repair Irvine</strong> residents need once it cools off.</p>

        <h2>Why Call One Company for Both</h2>
        <p>Most HVAC outfits lean one direction — they're either "the AC guys" or "the furnace guys." We do both, on purpose. Same techs who handle a dead capacitor in July are the ones diagnosing a furnace that won't ignite in December. So when you need <strong>air conditioning repair Irvine</strong> in the middle of a heat wave, or <strong>furnace repair Irvine</strong> when the heat's gone out overnight, it's the same number either way. Saves you the hassle of finding a second company six months later.</p>

        <h2>The Stuff That Actually Breaks</h2>
        <p>AC problems usually come down to a handful of things: a capacitor that's given out, a coil buried in dust, low refrigerant, sometimes a compressor that's just old and tired. That's most of what <strong>air conditioning repair Irvine</strong> calls turn out to be — weak airflow, the unit cycling on and off too much, bills creeping up with no real explanation.</p>
        <p>Furnaces fail differently. Pilot light won't hold. Ignitor's dead. Blower's making a grinding noise nobody likes. Or worse — a cracked heat exchanger, which is a safety issue, not just an inconvenience. A good chunk of <strong>furnace repair Irvine</strong> visits start with someone saying "it smells weird when it turns on," and that's always worth checking right away.</p>

        <h2>We Show Up Fast</h2>
        <p>Nobody wants to sit around for a week with no heat or no AC. Most jobs — whether it's <strong>air conditioning repair Irvine</strong> in August or <strong>furnace repair Irvine</strong> in January — get scheduled same-day or the next morning. Trucks carry common parts, so techs usually finish in one trip.</p>

        <h2>Local, and It Helps</h2>
        <p>We're based here, which matters more than people think. Irvine's older neighborhoods, newer builds, even certain HOA rules — all of it affects how HVAC systems age and what tends to break first. Every repair's done to code and backed by a guarantee. That's really the point of going local: someone's actually around if something needs a second look.</p>
        <p>Heat acting up, furnace gone quiet — either way, call HiLo Heating and Air. We'd rather fix it correctly the first time.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <Reviews client:visible />
    <BrandsSection />

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How soon can you come out for an AC issue?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Same-day most of the time, next-day at the latest during busy stretches.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Do you actually do furnace work, or mostly AC?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Both. Same technicians handle heating and cooling — no need to call two different companies.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">My furnace smells strange when it kicks on. Is that serious?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes — get it checked. Could be a cracked heat exchanger, which isn't something to wait on.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Will I get a price before any work starts?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, you'll see the cost upfront. No surprises on the bill afterward.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How often should the AC or furnace get inspected?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Once a year each, ideally before the season starts, so small issues don't turn into emergencies.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">What brands or systems do you work on?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Central air, mini-splits, heat pumps, standard furnaces — most major brands found in Irvine homes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Are technicians licensed?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, every one of them, fully licensed and insured.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">What happens if the issue comes back after a repair?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">It's covered under our guarantee — just give us a call.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-brand-blue/5 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-brand-blue font-semibold">HiLo Heating and Air · 8131 Electric Ave, Stanton, CA 90680, United States</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1"><a href="tel:+17148535534" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">(714) 853-5534</a> · <a href="mailto:info@hiloheatingandair.com" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">info@hiloheatingandair.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection client:visible />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
